<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Welcome to Beauty Beats</title>
    <style type="text/css">
      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        height: 100vh;
        min-width: 100%;
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.5;
        color: #222222;
      }

      a {
        color: #fff;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: 700;
        line-height: 1.25;
        margin-top: 0;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .status {
        color: #fff;
        width: 100px;
        padding: 10px;
        animation: blink 2s infinite;
        text-align: center;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }

      @keyframes blink {
        from {
          opacity: 0;
        }

        to {
          opacity: 1;
        }
      }

      p {
        margin-top: 0;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
      }

      .divider {
        border-top: 1px solid #ccc;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }

      .email-wrapper {
        max-width: 700px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: #fff;
        padding: 20px;
      }

      .email-header {
        background-color: #1e1e1e;
        padding: 30px;
        color: #f086d9;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .email-body {
        padding: 14px;
        background-color: #f4f3f3;
        height: 70vh;
      }

      .email-footer {
        background-color: #1e1e1e;
        padding: 14px;
        color: #d55fbb;
        text-align: center;
      }

      img {
        padding: 24px;
        max-width: 100%;
        height: auto;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
      <div class="email-header">
        <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dap91fhxh/image/upload/v1723705045/Beatslogo1_hefbyn.png" height="200px" width="200px" alt="">
      </div>
      <div class="email-body">
        <p>Hello <%= name %>,</p>
        <p>We are thrilled to welcome you to Beauty Beats, your new go-to destination for all things beauty. We're here to help you discover products that match your style and elevate your beauty routine.</p>
        <p>Stay tuned for exclusive offers, beauty tips, and the latest trends directly in your inbox.</p>
        <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, feel free to <a href="<%= supportLink %>">contact us</a>.</p>
        <p>Thank you for joining us. Let's make beauty Beatsful!</p>
      </div>
      <div class="email-footer">
        <p>&copy;2024 Beauty Beats. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>